The scripts in this folder will:
1) Download cloud image
2) Create a temp VM
3) Copy install and setup scripts to VM
4) Install usefull performance tools and sample scripts
5) Undefine temp VM, leave the altered .qcow2 image intact

Usage:

x_create_backing_image.sh

(This will create the backing image and may only be done once. VM's will be created using this backing image)

y_create_vm_from_backing.sh

(This will create one VM using the backing image that was created with x_create_backing_image.sh)

Notes:
Files and scripts may be added to the folder "vm_scripts" This folder gets copied into the image and will thus be available in all VM's
